Chef Wanted with Anne Burrell - Season 3, Episode 8




Vegas Showdown

When Las Vegas hot spot Dos Cominos is looking for a new Executive Chef, Anne Burrell brings four candidates to vie for the job. Before two chefs are given the keys to restaurant for a night of dinner service, the chefs are first tested on creating their unique take on a sweet and spicy taco and creating and demo-ing a signature guacamole.




Original Air Date: 19-Sep-2013
